Version 0.4.0
-------------
* Updated API documentation
* Fixed the tests to the updated Zibo API
* Request: cleaned up the fromXMLString method
* Value: getting the XML of a struct value will return a <nil /> element instead of an empty and thus invalid <struct /> element

Version 0.3.1
-------------
* xmlrpc_request.rng: params contains zeroOrMore param tags and not oneOrMore 
* Server: made error messages a bit clearer
* Value: improved converting to integer in convertValue 

Version 0.3.0
-------------
* Server: opened more for inheritance and extended parameter handling
* Value: added convertValue to cast values to a different type if possible 
* Value: better nil and array handling
* Response: using zibo dom document
* ExtendedServer: added system.multicall service
* throw XmlRpcInvalidResponseException when the response xml does not conform the rng schema
* make sure there is an error message when a service throws an exception

Version 0.2.2
-------------
* added XmlRpcInvalidResponseException